00:01:08.002 --> 00:01:09.441
Which is why it's so, like,

00:01:09.442 --> 00:01:12.561
infuriating to know that this one governor is able to take, like,

00:01:12.562 --> 00:01:14.561
this entire state from 2024 back to,

00:01:14.562 --> 00:01:15.721
